    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything i spent fifteen years on... the whole theory, the data, the legacy... it was all just wrong. i'm not just a failure, i'm a fraud. i look in the mirror and i don't even see a person anymore, just a mistake that needs to be corrected. there is nothing left for me here.",
