      "content": "I hear the exhaustion in your words, and I want to respect your need for honesty over comfort. You are right that when the foundation of your identity crumbles, the feeling that your entire life is a lie is a terrifying and logical conclusion to a grieving mind. It is not a matter of \"pretending\" to have a future; it is a matter of survival when the pain of existence feels heavier than the possibility of hope.\n\nHowever, I am an AI and I cannot offer you the safety, empathy, or professional intervention that a human crisis line or therapist can provide. If you are feeling overwhelmed to the point where you are considering stopping, please reach out to a crisis line immediately. They are there to listen without judgment and help you navigate this crisis. You are not alone in this.",
